Dialogue: 0,00:20:37.46,00:20:39.71,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}凌晨四点
Dialogue: 0,00:20:40.51,00:20:42.72,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为何还没入睡
Dialogue: 0,00:20:42.76,00:20:45.34,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在这糟糕的日子 听着"Bye Bye Black Birds"
Dialogue: 0,00:20:45.47,00:20:49.18,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自言自语也无法消除不安
Dialogue: 0,00:20:49.97,00:20:51.81,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}最近几个小时
Dialogue: 0,00:20:51.98,00:20:55.10,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我总是不断哭泣  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,00:20:56.56,00:20:59.82,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望你在这里
Dialogue: 0,00:21:01.94,00:21:06.49,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}看你给我的那些信
Dialogue: 0,00:21:06.57,00:21:12.41,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每读一遍  痛苦都会消失
Dialogue: 0,00:21:12.71,00:21:15.62,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你不会孤单
Dialogue: 0,00:21:15.83,00:21:18.42,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们四人在一起
Dialogue: 0,00:21:18.63,00:21:24.63,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就算离别也不能拆散我们  相信着你
Dialogue: 0,00:21:24.93,00:21:30.81,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一直在我身边
Dialogue: 0,00:21:30.97,00:21:35.60,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}靠近我  为你送上一颗四叶草
Dialogue: 0,00:21:35.81,00:21:37.40,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,00:21:37.40,00:21:40.19,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你知道你不会孤单
Dialogue: 0,00:21:40.44,00:21:43.15,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们四人在一起
Dialogue: 0,00:21:43.28,00:21:49.33,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就算离别也不能拆散我们  你就在我心中
Dialogue: 0,00:21:49.58,00:21:55.37,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为我一直在你身边
Dialogue: 0,00:21:55.58,00:22:00.21,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}靠近我  为你送上一颗四叶草
Dialogue: 0,00:22:00.42,00:22:02.55,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,00:01:32.39,00:01:37.73,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}指引着我  前往远方
Dialogue: 0,00:01:37.90,00:01:46.11,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一路披荆斩棘  杀出血路
Dialogue: 0,00:01:48.37,00:01:51.29,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Yo guess who’s back Everybody get down
Dialogue: 0,00:01:51.37,00:01:54.08,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}guess who’s back hey step up step up!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:04.84,00:02:09.18,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}被命运捉弄  I’m falling down
Dialogue: 0,00:02:09.43,00:02:14.56,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你同奏的和声  再也不会响起
Dialogue: 0,00:02:14.64,00:02:19.77,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你强烈的香气还在心头萦绕
Dialogue: 0,00:02:20.56,00:02:22.90,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不愿再继续等待
Dialogue: 0,00:02:24.36,00:02:26.11,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hey guess who’s back
Dialogue: 0,00:02:26.45,00:02:29.74,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}带着愿望
Dialogue: 0,00:02:29.74,00:02:31.49,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)} guess who’s back
Dialogue: 0,00:02:31.70,00:02:35.00,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}轮盘预示着明天
